name: Rocket Launch Sequence
description:
To Play: Press the Keyboard E Button at the Main Control Panel for more time! Complete all of the puzzles around the space station before time runs out!

After completing the puzzles make sure you go up to the window to watch the rocket!

This is my first Ludum dare! I hope you all enjoy my game as I worked very hard to complete it in a limited amount of time! If you want to see more of my work check out my youtube channel! 

TimmyJTech
